title: 1990 United Malays National Organisation leadership election
text:
A leadership election was held by the <a href="United%20Malays%20National%20Organisation">United Malays National Organisation</a> (UMNO) party on 30 November 1990. It was won by incumbent Prime Minister and President of UMNO, <a href="Mahathir%20Mohamad">Mahathir Mohamad</a>.
Supreme Council election results.
<a href="http%3A//studentsrepo.um.edu.my/1735/7/BAB_5.pdf">Source</a>
Vice Presidents.
6 other candidates withdrawn, including <a href="Najib%20Razak">Najib Razak</a> and <a href="Abu%20Hassan%20Omar">Abu Hassan Omar</a>.
